author: Soraya Joseph
title: 21 Outrageous Celebrity Pregnancy Cravings
text:
21 Outrageous Celebrity Pregnancy Cravings What the fork? Some of these preggo celebrity cravings are pretty bizarre. by Soraya Joseph 1 h ago 
When eating for a party of two (and in some cases, three), there are no limits to what your tastebuds crave. Just ask these celebrity mamas who know a thing or two about outrageous pregnancy cravings. From pumpkin ice-cream with pickles on the side, to fries dunked in milkshakes, check out what Beyoncé , Ciara , Mariah Carey and more craved while expecting. 
Raw fish may be on the list of “no-no’s” if you’re preggo, but that doesn’t mean you can’t take a look at it. Check out Martha Stewart surprising Snoop Dogg with a sushi cake.
